summary: This is an email from the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit containing a draft arrest report (302) for Ghislaine Maxwell. The email indicates the document is not finalized and requests feedback.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell
persons.context: She is the subject of the drafted arrest 302 document attached to the email.

events.title: Drafting of Ghislaine Maxwell Arrest Report
events.description: The FBI New York Field Office drafts an arrest 302 report for Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: A draft arrest report (302) for Ghislaine Maxwell was created by the FBI New York Field Office's Child Exploitation/Human Trafficking unit on July 10, 2020.
The document was not finalized at the time of the email, indicating it was still under review.
The email and attachments are part of the official case records (EFTA00078754).
